        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="js"><a href="#js" class="headerlink" title="js"></a>js</h1><h3 id="事件"><a href="#事件" class="headerlink" title="事件"></a>事件</h3><ol><li><p>点击事件</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="title function_">addEventListener</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;click&#x27;</span>,<span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)&#123;&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​</p></li><li><p>鼠标事件</p><ul><li>鼠标经过</li></ul><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="title function_">addEventListener</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;mouseenter&#x27;</span>,<span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)&#123;&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>鼠标移开</li></ul><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="title function_">addEventListener</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;mouseleave&#x27;</span>,<span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)&#123;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​</p></li><li><p>键盘事件</p><ul><li>键盘输入</li></ul><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="title function_">addEventListener</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;keyup&#x27;</span>,<span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)&#123;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>页面加载事件</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">windows.<span class="title function_">addEventListener</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;load&#x27;</span>,<span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)&#123;&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">addEventListener</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;DomContentLoaded , function()&#123;&#125;&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/js.assets/1710243660844.png" alt="71024366084"></p></li><li><p>页面滚动事件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">window.addEventListener(&#x27;scroll&#x27;  , function()&#123;&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/js.assets/1710244411297.png" alt="71024441129"></p></li></ol><h3 id="日期对象"><a href="#日期对象" class="headerlink" title="日期对象"></a>日期对象</h3><ol><li><p>获取对象的方法</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 获得日期对象</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> date = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Date</span>()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 使用里面的方法</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(date.<span class="title function_">getFullYear</span>())</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(date.<span class="title function_">getMonth</span>() + <span class="number">1</span>)  <span class="comment">// 月份要 + 1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(date.<span class="title function_">getDate</span>())</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(date.<span class="title function_">getDay</span>())  <span class="comment">// 星期几</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>将毫秒数转换成对应年月日的方法</p><p><img src="/img/js.assets/1710315667594.png" alt="71031566759"></p></li></ol><h3 id="节点操作"><a href="#节点操作" class="headerlink" title="节点操作"></a>节点操作</h3><ol><li><p>Dom节点</p><p><img src="/img/js.assets/1710429140342.png" alt="71042914034"></p></li><li><p>查找节点</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//儿子节点</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> baby = <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;.baby&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(baby)  <span class="comment">// 返回dom对象</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(baby.<span class="property">parentNode</span>)  <span class="comment">// 返回父节点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(baby.<span class="property">parentNode</span>.<span class="property">parentNode</span>)  <span class="comment">// 返回爷节点</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>增加节点</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//生成父节点</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> fa = <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;.father&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//生成子节点</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> son = <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">createElement</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;.son&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//添加，注：默认添加到末尾</span></span><br><span class="line">fa.<span class="title function_">appendChild</span>(son)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//若要添加到头部</span></span><br><span class="line">fa.<span class="title function_">insertBefore</span>(son, son.<span class="property">children</span>[<span class="number">0</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>克隆节点</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//获取元素</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> ul =  <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;ul&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//克隆 , true:将标签以及内容都克隆 ，false:仅克隆标签</span></span><br><span class="line"> ul.<span class="title function_">appendChild</span>(ul.<span class="property">children</span>[<span class="number">0</span>].<span class="title function_">cloneNode</span>(<span class="literal">true</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="DOM对象与BOM对象"><a href="#DOM对象与BOM对象" class="headerlink" title="DOM对象与BOM对象"></a>DOM对象与BOM对象</h3><ol><li><p>DOM对象</p><p><img src="/img/js.assets/1710429413481.png" alt="71042941348"></p></li><li><p>BOM对象</p><p><img src="/img/js.assets/1710429463840.png" alt="71042946384"></p><ol><li><p>localtion对象</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> href 经常用href 利用js的方法去跳转页面</span><br><span class="line">   location.<span class="property">href</span> = <span class="string">&#x27;http://www.baidu.com&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>本地存储localStorage</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//向本地存储中存储数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">localStorage</span>.<span class="title function_">setItem</span>(key, value)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//向本地存储中获取数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">localStorage</span>.<span class="title function_">getItem</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;key&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//删除本地存储中的key</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable language_">localStorage</span>.<span class="title function_">removeItem</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;object&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>存储复杂数据类型时,因本地只能存储字符串，所以存储到本地存储时若存取为对象，则需要把对象转化成字符串，转换方法如下：</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title class_">JSON</span>.<span class="title function_">stringify</span>(复杂数据类型)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>当拿出本地存储的数据时则需要将JSON字符串转换为对象，方法如下：</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title class_">JSON</span>.<span class="title function_">parse</span>(<span class="variable language_">localStorage</span>.<span class="title function_">getItem</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;key&#x27;</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​</p></li></ul></li></ol></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
